msgid "Workflow"
msgstr "Flux de travail"

msgid ""
"Record-triggered workflow rules with field conditions, immediate actions "
"(update field, assign task, email, notification), and time-based triggers "
"scheduled relative to record or rule dates."
msgstr ""
"Regles de flux de travail declenchees par des enregistrements avec des "
"conditions de champ, des actions immediates (mettre a jour le champ, "
"assigner une tache, e-mail, notification) et des declencheurs temporels "
"planifies par rapport aux dates des enregistrements ou des regles."

msgid ""
"Migrated signal imports to the horilla.db.models.signals shim and "
"standardized first-party import groups; behavior unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Migration des imports de signaux vers le shim horilla.db.models.signals et "
"standardisation des groupes d'imports internes ; comportement inchange."

msgid ""
"Workflow automation engine: WorkflowRule / WorkflowCondition / "
"WorkflowAction models, dynamic condition evaluation, immediate dispatch on "
"record saves, Celery WorkflowTimeTriggerAction and "
"ScheduledWorkflowExecution, execution history modal, FilterSet support, auto-"
"registration for workflow-enabled CRM models (leads, accounts, campaigns, "
"contacts, opportunities), modular views, hidden-field action configuration "
"fixes, restored workflow detail pages, and improved routing namespaces."
msgstr ""
"Moteur d'automatisation des flux de travail : modeles WorkflowRule / "
"WorkflowCondition / WorkflowAction, evaluation dynamique des conditions, "
"distribution immediate lors de la sauvegarde des enregistrements, Celery "
"WorkflowTimeTriggerAction et ScheduledWorkflowExecution, modal d'historique "
"d'execution, support FilterSet, enregistrement automatique pour les modeles "
"CRM."

msgid ""
"WorkflowRuleForm aligned with HorillaModelForm layout: field_order, Meta."
"fields = \"__all__\", and keep_on_form for is_active; action forms unchanged."
msgstr ""
"WorkflowRuleForm aligne sur le layout HorillaModelForm : field_order, "
"Meta.fields et keep_on_form pour is_active ; formulaires d'action inchanges."

msgid ""
"Initial release: workflow rules per ContentType with create/edit triggers, "
"AND/OR conditions, ordered immediate actions, time-trigger actions with "
"Celery scheduling and execution history, Settings → Automations → Workflow "
"Rules, and integration with registered CRM models via feature registration."
msgstr ""
"Version initiale : regles de flux de travail par ContentType avec "
"declencheurs de creation/edition, conditions AND/OR, actions immediates "
"ordonnees, actions de declencheur temporel avec planification Celery et "
"historique d'execution, Parametres → Automatisations → Regles de flux."

